1. *Pokušamo* da rešimo ovaj problem zajedno. (We try to solve this problem together.)
2. Da li smo *pokušali* da kontaktiramo te ljude? (Have we tried to contact those people?)
3. Molim te, *pokušaj* ponovo. (Please try again.)
4. Ako *pokušate* da uradite ovo, dobićete odgovor. (If you try to do this, you will get an answer.)
5. Ne znam da li ćemo uspeti, ali moramo *pokušati*. (I don't know if we'll succeed, but we have to try.)
6. *Pokušavao* sam da vas kontaktiram, ali niste odgovorili. (I tried to contact you, but you didn't respond.)
7. Da li bi *pokušali* da mi pomognete? (Would you try to help me?)
8. Mislim da treba *pokušati* drugi pristup. (I think we should try a different approach.)
9. Nadam se da ćeš *pokušati* da razumeš moju situaciju. (I hope you'll try to understand my situation.)
10. *Pokušaću* da završim ovaj projekat pre roka. (I'll try to finish this project before the deadline.)